reviewText:
The 3-pack consists of three films that are unrelated other than having the word "doctor" in the title. In the third film, the doctor is a good guy and not that deadly. The first two films are horror with blood while DOCTOR MORDRID is akin to a SyFy production.

The films are all campy/cheesy and some people consider them to be cult classics.

Guide: F-bombs, sex, and nudity.
